  <section class="fyre-comment-body">
    <div class="fyre-comment">
      <p><p>Hi Mhairi,
I meant to get in touch earlier but I had a big essay reply planned from my point of view of the situation but it wasn't worth it because I agree with most things you say in this blog its just that the events aren't accurate, as ,to be fair ,you had entered the situation when I had already been branded "sexist" (which I found hard to take)so obviously all guns were a-blazing. I'm not going to go into detail recalling specifics and defending my words as it was a long time ago. All I want to say is I'm not as naive to the workings of the world as you may think and that I have absolutely no hard feelings as I appreciate a call out and like to challange things especially prejudice comments which is why I was able to take the 'angry mob'. Anyway I just want you to know that if we meet again its all good in da hood. Mark</p></p>
    </div>
    
